body:
![Icon](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chromebookbob/Nebulaic-Toaster-Kivy/master/data/icon.png)
### Welcome to Nebulaic_Toaster.
A game in development.

Nebulaic_Toaster is the second iteration of the text based game of the same name (see: https://github.com/chromebookbob/nebulaic-toaster). It is written in kivy and I will be releasing it on as many platforms as possible.

### Authors and Contributors
chromebookbob
